<h2 id="logo-on-color">Logo on color</h2>
<p>In certain situations, the logo can also be used on a white or contextually colored background, as long as there is a 3:1 contrast ratio. Anything less may compromise visibility and is not recommended. Color contrasts can be checked here- https://webaim.org/resources/contrastchecker/</p>
